contentBlocks.value: We all know its true, WA has the best greens, and by that i mean barley, but no leaf thanks. Alby is a good classic draught beer at a good price. With an alcohol content of 4.2% you'll probably need a bit of 4.20% to get you a bit messed up, but that's okay. If people catch you with this in your hand it's nothing to be ashamed of.
